{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Diagnostics (Universal)\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook provides a universal diagnostics workflow that works for **any ML type**\n",
    "(binary classification, multiclass, regression, time-to-event).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Part 1 — Study Overview** (via `predict/notebook_utils`): study details, performance metrics, selected features.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Part 2 — Feature Importances** (via `diagnostics`): saved FI parquet files, filterable by method, dataset, etc.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Part 3 — Optuna Diagnostics** (via `diagnostics`): trial counts, trials scatter, hyperparameters.\n",
    "\n",
    "No model loading is performed."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Imports"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from octopus.predict.notebook_utils import (\n",
    "    find_latest_study,\n",
    "    show_study_details,\n",
    "    show_target_metric_performance,\n",
    "    show_selected_features,\n",
    ")\n",
    "from octopus.diagnostics import StudyDiagnostics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Input"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "study_name_prefix = \"wf_octo_mrmr_octo\"\n",
    "studies_root = \"../studies\"\n",
    "\n",
    "study_directory = find_latest_study(studies_root, study_name_prefix)\n",
    "print(f\"Using study: {study_directory}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Part 1: Study Overview"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Study Details"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "study_info = show_study_details(study_directory)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Target Metric Performance"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "performance_tables = show_target_metric_performance(study_info)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Selected Features Summary"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "feature_table, freq_table, raw = show_selected_features(study_info)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Part 2: Feature Importances (from saved results)\n",
    "\n",
    "Two-step workflow:\n",
    "1. **`get_feature_importances()`** — load raw FI data filtered by task/module (returns a DataFrame)\n",
    "2. **`plot_feature_importance()`** — plot the FI data with additional filters (fi_method, fi_dataset, etc.)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag = StudyDiagnostics(study_info[\"path\"])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Load raw FI data for task 0"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fi_table = diag.get_feature_importances(task_id=0, result_type=\"best\")\n",
    "print(f\"FI rows: {len(fi_table)}\")\n",
    "for col in [\"fi_method\", \"fi_dataset\", \"training_id\", \"module\", \"outersplit_id\"]:\n",
    "    if col in fi_table.columns:\n",
    "        print(f\"  {col}: {sorted(fi_table[col].unique().tolist())}\")\n",
    "fi_table.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Internal Feature Importance (train set)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_feature_importance(fi_table, fi_method=\"internal\", fi_dataset=\"train\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Permutation Feature Importance (dev set)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_feature_importance(fi_table, fi_method=\"permutation\", fi_dataset=\"dev\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Single outersplit view"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_feature_importance(fi_table, fi_method=\"internal\", outersplit_id=0, top_n=15)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Part 3: Optuna Diagnostics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Number of Unique Trials by Model Type"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_optuna_trial_counts()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Optuna Trials: Objective Value and Best Value"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_optuna_trials(outersplit_id=0, task_id=0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Optuna Hyperparameters"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "diag.plot_optuna_hyperparameters(outersplit_id=0, task_id=0)"
   ]
  }
 ],
